now available as well. This beta release adds support for
<a href="https://www.hardkernel.com/shop/odroid-n2-with-4gbyte-ram/">Hardkernel’s ODROID-N2</a>!</p>
<p>The <a href="https://www.hardkernel.com/shop/odroid-n2-with-4gbyte-ram/">ODROID-N2</a>
is a great and powerful alternative for the Raspberry Pi.</p>
